graph LR
    subgraph Session
        Hook[Lifecycle Hooks]
        Agent[Agent Work]
    end
    subgraph Memory["Memory MCP"]
        Curated[(memory.json Curated)]
        Obs[(observations.jsonl session.id + trace_id + span_id)]
    end
    subgraph Chronograph["Chronograph MCP"]
        ES[EventStore In-memory]
        OTel[OTel Exporter session.id on every span]
    end
    Phoenix[(Arize Phoenix SQLite)]

    Hook -->|inject_memory| Agent
    Agent -->|remember| Curated
    Hook -->|capture_session| Obs
    Hook -->|capture_memory + trace context| Obs
    Hook -.->|send_event HTTP| ES
    ES --> OTel
    OTel -.->|OTLP| Phoenix
    Agent -->|recall/search| Curated
